            <div class="camping-option">
                <h3>Camping</h3>
                <p class="section-content">Experience the great outdoors with our scenic camping sites. Nestled in lush greenery, our campsites offer a perfect blend of adventure and tranquility. Enjoy modern amenities like clean restrooms, showers, and fire pits, ensuring a comfortable and memorable stay under the stars.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center description" id="campers">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="camping-option">
                <h3>Campers</h3>
                <p class="section-content">Stay in one of our fully equipped campers for a cozy and convenient getaway. Each camper features a comfortable sleeping area, kitchenette, and dining space, providing all the comforts of home in a compact and mobile setup. Ideal for those looking to explore the area with ease and flexibility.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center description" id="bungallows">
        <div class="col-md-12">
